sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as RayCluster Controller
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>GCS: 6379/TCP<br/>Dashboard: 8265/TCP
    participant WorkerPods as Ray Worker Pods
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation and Pod Lifecycle

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create RayCluster<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>mTLS
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Validation response
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>mTLS
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Mutation response (inject defaults)

    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event: RayCluster created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Head Service<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    WorkerPods->>HeadPod: Connect to GCS<br/>6379/TCP (mTLS optional)

    Note over User,WorkerPods: Flow 2: RayJob Submission

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create RayJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event: RayJob created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>HeadPod: Submit job via dashboard API<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    HeadPod->>WorkerPods: Distribute tasks<br/>GCS protocol
    WorkerPods-->>HeadPod: Task results
    Controller->>HeadPod: Poll job status<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update RayJob status<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,OAuthServer: Flow 3: Dashboard Access with OAuth

    User->>K8sAPI: Browser → OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI->>HeadPod: Route to oauth-proxy sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    HeadPod->>OAuthServer: Validate OAuth token<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    OAuthServer-->>HeadPod: Token validation response
    HeadPod->>HeadPod: Forward to Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    HeadPod-->>User: Dashboard UI<br/>OAuth session cookie
